    "For online learning, we follow (Meng et al., 2024) and use prompts from Ultra-Feedback.",
    "We summarize the datasets used in Appendix B.3.",
    "Evaluation Benchmarks To holistically evaluate our models performance, we follow prior work and consider in total four benchmarks: Arena-Hard-Auto (Li et al., 2024), AlpacaEval-2 (Dubois et al., 2024; Li et al., 2023b), MT-Bench (Zheng et al., 2023), and OpenLLM (Beeching et al., 2023).",
